title: Chipotle
typeOfFood: Lacto, Fast food, Take-out, Mexican, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. U.S.-based fast food chain where you could customize your order (tacos, burritos, bowls) and request no cheese/dairy. Has brown rice, white rice, black beans, pinto beans, cooked veggies, salsas, guacamole and salad. The vegan options don't have to pay the surcharge of for guacamole, as it's include it in the price since there is no meat inside.
